{"tid":870022,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)鬼入侵","createTime":"2018-10-20T17:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T19:45:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"969d230ff6210c15f9396abc1bfa3066f85cb933","tid":870022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:39:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=af668f9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3959c204\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5462d999\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/4aa7n345ef4xkxpt1444830959.jpg/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fvcover_vt_pic%2F0%2F4aa7n345ef4xkxpt1444830959.jpg%2F0&h=3f8816d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年屆不惑的女子伊琳諾&middot;蘭斯（莉莉&middot;泰勒 Lili Taylor 飾）生活一塌糊塗，她犧牲自己的幸福，十幾年裡悉心照顧患病在床的母親。母親去世後，妹妹簡（Virginia Madsen 飾）又圖謀奪取她的房產。走投無路之時，伊琳諾從報紙上看到一則失眠研究所的志願者徵詢廣告，受徵詢金額的吸引，她決定報名參加。與之異同應徵的還有西奧&middot;多娜（凱瑟琳&middot;澤塔&middot;瓊斯Catherine Zeta-Jones 飾）與盧克&middot;桑德森（Owen Wilson 飾），在發起人馬洛教授（連姆&middot;尼森Liam Neeson飾）的帶領下，他們來到了一座建成已有上百年的莊園<br />\n<br />\n1 50AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 播完係到電視劇版<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4ab7c291\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=6QwtPriUDP2xM9PYNmK9OYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=fc8eb82c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dd9e5e706218938d98297589a784e341d07d20","tid":870022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266e5a9978c253c94c33fa783bf6f7ac8e234c6e","tid":870022,"uid":215675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9810e7a404dec832846538c86747c0f820670b13","tid":870022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"266e5a9978c253c94c33fa783bf6f7ac8e234c6e","tid":870022,"uid":215675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"此